data.description: OPEN HOUSE  SUNDAY 1/30! Welcome Home!! This must-see 3 bedroom, 2 full bath split level home is situated in an extremely convenient Westminster location. Inside a neighborhood but close to commuter routes and Westminster High School House!  Well-updated with an upgraded kitchen, featuring granite counters and stainless appliances, an eat-in kitchen along with a breakfast bar. The rear deck is accessed right through the kitchen/dining area for outside living. Hardwoods throughout the entire first floor. Upstairs you will discover 3 full bedrooms (also all hardwood!) and a remodeled ceramic bath with a skylight. The primary bedroom features a walk-in closet!  Beautifully finished lower-level family room area with custom built-ins, gorgeous flooring, and an updated full bath. Perfect for family gatherings! The large fenced backyard is ideal for pets, and the storage shed/man cave with electricity is the icing on the cake. All new HVAC system in 2019, and new water heater in 2017.
